  "description": "This roast vegetable salad is a hybrid of Greek salad and Fattoush salad, which is a Middle Eastern bread salad, traditionally made with pita. This warm version uses cooked red onion, courgette and tomatoes which are gently tumbled together with crisped tortillas shards, fresh dill and a slab of oregano baked feta. Release your inner Greek!",
